list

public Adsense.Accounts.List list()
                           throws IOException
List all accounts available to this AdSense account. Create a request for the method "accounts.list". This request holds the parameters needed by the the adsense server. After setting any optional parameters, call the Adsense.Accounts.List.execute() method to invoke the remote operation.

Returns:
the request
Throws:
IOException - if the initialization of the request fails

get

public Adsense.Accounts.Get get(String accountId)
                         throws IOException
Get information about the selected AdSense account. Create a request for the method "accounts.get". This request holds the parameters needed by the the adsense server. After setting any optional parameters, call the Adsense.Accounts.Get.execute() method to invoke the remote operation.

Parameters:
accountId - Account to get information about.
Returns:
the request
Throws:
IOException - if the initialization of the request fails
